Diary of Lydia:

I do not know why I'm here! I think he knows all my most secret secrets! He asked me what I do not want to leave. I was Cesna with him, but I can not remember what I said. All that was ... I lost it! Make that really happen? He requested that I gave all of myself to this! He accused me of betraying my family, my life, my God, and even the natural law!

"I do not know what you are!"
